reviewText: Love this show. Wish season 4 was on DVD

Life with Derek continues with its second season and brings even more laughs. Casey and Derek continue there battle for power over the house. I really like these episodes and I can't wait for the next season.
My son was a huge fan of this show that was on Disney Channel. Was thrilled I could buy seasons for him. I enjoy watching them with him actually! Great deal!

I just love Life With Derek ever since it was shown on The Disney Channel now I get to see the original Canadian Version plus tons of extras. Cant wait to get seasons 3 and 4 plus Vacation with Derek.
I purchased this as a gift for my daughter.  She really likes it.  I watched it with her and I think it's a cute show.

I couldn't wait for the DVDs to come out for season 2. It was one of my favorite. The dvds are similar to the first one. It's a complete season with some behind the scenes extras. In terms of quality, it's better than watching them directly on tv. I know this isn't that helpful, so I'm sorry.
